{
  "stem": "10710.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that Leopold, the commander, wanted to dispose of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Wanted to burn them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There should be no sign left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Schindler didn't let him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He bought a piece of cemetery in the town, and they had a Jewish burial.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We said Kaddish for them and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he was always-- Schindler when everything happened something he was always there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then and once Goeth came to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You know, Goeth was put to jail for all this black market things what he did in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He took so much money from the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he was buying all kind of gold and silver.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "People were making jokes of him, the prisoners, our people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He couldn't do anything anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Because he wasn't in charge anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Schindler was in charge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Schindler used to take his truck and used to go to organize food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Wherever they had some factories he used to bring in loaves of bread to us, all kind of food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "He just went in the morning with the Jewish affair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "He knew where to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he brought all kind of stuff we should have enough food to eat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And people who survived Schindler, you have my picture there, when I was there they all looked pretty well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Not like the Muselmanns from other camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Muselmann is a person who is a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you became a Muselmann if you didn't take care of yourself, if you didn't wash, and you didn't care for yourself, you didn't do anything, then you become officially a Muselmann, and it was the end of you.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you didn't take care of your-- you became I would say, resigned from life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't care what happens to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
